Privacy Policy for "Family Face Finder"

Last Updated: November 23, 2024

Introduction
Welcome to "Family Face Finder" We take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our app. By using "Family Face Finder", you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

"Family Face Finder" does not collect or store personal data. However, the app may access certain information locally on your device to function as intended.

Photos and Media:
The app accesses your device’s photo library to select images for gameplay. This access is required for the app’s functionality, and no images are uploaded, stored, or shared outside your device.
User-Provided Data:
Any names or labels added to photos are stored locally on your device. This information is not transmitted to external servers. 2. How We Use Your Information

"Family Face Finder" processes information locally on your device for the following purposes:

To allow you to select and display photos for the game.
To enhance your experience through personalized gameplay. 3. Data Sharing

"Family Face Finder" does not share your data with third parties. All data remains on your device, ensuring maximum privacy.

4. Permissions Required

To use the app’s features, you may need to grant the following permissions:

Photo Library Access: To select images for gameplay.
You can revoke these permissions at any time through your device’s settings.

5. Data Security

We take appropriate measures to protect the data stored on your device. However, as no data is transmitted externally, the security of your information depends on the security of your device.

6. Children's Privacy

"Family Face Finder" is designed to be child-friendly. We do not collect or share any personal information from children under 13. All data is processed locally on the device.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app, and your continued use of the app constitutes acceptance of these changes.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: vendorhelperapp@gmail.com

By using "Family Face Finder", you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy. Thank you for trusting us with your privacy!
